---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Comffordable Air Solutions" description="Learn more about Comffordable Air Solutions and our dedication to providing premium HVAC repair and maintenance in the Tampa Bay Area.">
    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero"
            style="min-height: 60vh; align-items: center;">
            <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="Comffordable Air Solutions HVAC technician working on a unit" class="hero-bg-img" loading="eager" width="1200" height="800" />
            <div class="hero-overlay" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.65), rgba(0,0,0,0.8));"></div>
            <div class="container hero-content text-center" style="margin: 0 auto;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 4.5rem; text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our <span
                        class="text-purple">Story.</span></h1>
                <p
                    style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.5rem; text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); max-width: 800px;">
                    Unwavering dedication to your home's comfort.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Content -->
        <section class="process-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="services-grid" style="align-items: center;">
                    <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Your Trusted HVAC Partner</h2>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">I take immense pride in delivering honest, high-quality work that you can count on. My family, especially my daughter and my mom, is my greatest motivation and the reason I strive to grow every single day, both personally and professionally. I truly believe in treating people with fairness and respect, because doing right by others is the only way to build lasting trust and long-term relationships.</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">My approach to business is simple: be straightforward, communicate clearly, and always stand behind what I do. I don’t believe in cutting corners or overcomplicating things. It’s about doing the job right the first time so you can feel completely confident in your home's comfort.</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">When I’m not working, you’ll usually find me staying active outdoors. Whether I’m out on my bicycle or embarking on a new adventure, I love to stay driven and challenge myself. At the end of the day, I’m committed to providing reliable service and earning your trust with every visit.</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;"><strong class="text-purple">Comffordable Air Solutions</strong> is more than just a quick fix. We optimize your system's performance, protecting your home investment for years to come throughout <a href="/service-areas/st-petersburg-fl" class="text-purple" style="font-weight: 600;">St. Petersburg</a>, <a href="/service-areas/tampa-fl" class="text-purple" style="font-weight: 600;">Tampa</a>, and <a href="/service-areas/clearwater-fl" class="text-purple" style="font-weight: 600;">Clearwater</a>.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <img src="/images/jeremy.png"
                            alt="Jeremy, Comffordable Air Solutions lead HVAC technician"
                            style="width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>



        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section
            style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark), var(--bg-darker)); text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);">
            <div class="container animate-on-scroll">
                <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Experience Comffordable Air</h2>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 1rem 2rem; position: relative;">Contact Us Today</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
